ray.rage.rendersystem.shader

Interface GpuShaderProgram.Context

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Disposable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GlslProgramContext
    Enclosing interface:
    GpuShaderProgram

    public static interface GpuShaderProgram.Context
extends Disposable
    The context encapsulates all the objects whose information is needed by the program to execute properly.

    This is basically a data container for program arguments. However, it does so in away that avoids polluting the program interface.

    Author:
    Raymond L. Rivera
